            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>
                    [Front face]: To our master Galerius Valerius Maximinus, the most noble Caesar. Ulpius Alenus, the most perfect man, correct of Apulia and Calabria, devoted to his divine force and majesty.
                    [Left face]: Dedicated on the 5th day before the Nones of March, when Aemilianus (for the second time) and Aquilinus were consuls.
                </p>
